        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/duanmuyi/" class="name">小波福娃</a>

            <span class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>

        <span content="2007-10-18" class="main-meta">2007-10-18 15:04:30</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1058234/">南海出版公司2004版</a>
